{"tid":1850542,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"身分證比人影低左可以點搞","createTime":"2020-01-29T14:55:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T06:16:45.000Z","uid":106899,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b78aa7cb9220ee339c4cb5c81cb5b440e270c5a4","tid":1850542,"uid":106899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T14:55:35.000Z","msg":"最近發現我屋企人用左我個名去電話公司上台<br />\n原來佢影左我身分證去搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（估唔到原來身分證副本可以做到咁多野）<br />\n我諗佢可能仲自製左授權信再拎埋住址證明之類<br />\n依家上台都事小 唔知之後佢又會無啦啦做d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇巴打知道可以點搞<br />\n我報失身分證再換過張有冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5281890ff1cc588cf7f5327b63c0343b719e24","tid":1850542,"uid":74368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T14:57:17.000Z","msg":"上連登開post問"},{"pid":"c52506f5e77673828a6caf049b010308d2654560","tid":1850542,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T14:57:46.000Z","msg":"幫你借錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc78d85f0f27a9e0beaaa082ddeb845ca27e0918","tid":1850542,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T14:58:03.000Z","msg":"告佢偽造假文書"},{"pid":"1b674fb5e62ba23f22dafec516836dca6156ce74","tid":1850542,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T14:58:33.000Z","msg":"身份證副本劃線<br />\n寫copy，並寫只限用於XX用途日期<br />\n簽名<br />\n<br />\n無呢啲唔認數是常識吧"},{"pid":"5870d40beca47287ed81257265ec5d8f0be8d6d9","tid":1850542,"uid":17566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T14:58:47.000Z","msg":"細佬妹嗎？咁大膽?"},{"pid":"504d794ab9b2cab54c6baacbba69cfcc2372161a","tid":1850542,"uid":325023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T14:59:08.000Z","msg":"換身份證 issue date唔同咗應該有用"},{"pid":"e422dcdec4124e394cae4be39ac7fa130d340da5","tid":1850542,"uid":37097,"like":